title: A way out of The Matrix? Don't be fooled by them.

author: Glink
description:
As the proverbial Cave from Plato's analogy, YouTube provides a place for viewers to sit and watch the shadows on the wall while the creators use the fire to depict them. Many have never left the cave, trapped in and enedless cycle of mindless entertainment with no sense of direction or purpose. In this darkness, there are those who've found a way out of the cave, but that is not where the story of Plato's Cave ends...
